Wake On Lan
===========

A small application to wake systems up from the lan. This is a small light weight C application that will run on most unix's, tested on: Mac OS X, OpenSolaris, Linux.

Installation
------------

- make
- install bin/wol /usr/local/bin

Usage
-----

Usage: wol <mac_address>

The mac address must be separated with colons (:). Such as 01:23:45:67:89:AB.
